data.description: Stunning views of Lake Kapowsin, Mt. Rainier, and surrounding timberland abound from this stately property perched on a private 20 acres. Gated community offers security and no visible neighbors so you can escape it all while still being close to amenities. Enter to a grand staircase, foyer and office. Great natural light pours through living room windows and sparkles off the hardwoods installed throughout the main level. Eat-in kitchen with oversized island and granite countertops. Formal dining space. Primary suites on both the main and upper levels with adjacent baths. Massive basement space for storage, home gym, and more! Acreage zoned forestry for lower taxes. Can heat with wood stove for lower energy costs. Not a driveby!
